channel.title: Who else is tired of Project Insanity servers?
channel.description:
I don't want this to be a rant, well, it sort of is... Does anyone else find that Project Insanity servers are starting to get really annoying?
I know that they're very easy to learn off of for beginners, but why does everyone choose it?
(pls no hate)
